{#
  Overview section: scan metadata, TOC, scope paragraph and a
  methodology callout box.

  Context:
    toc_entries    list[{ "num": "1", "title": "...", "anchor": "overview" }]
    target_kind    str
    target_locator str
    producer       str
    started_at     datetime
    finished_at    datetime
    duration_seconds  float
    finding_total  int
    methodology_version str
#}
<section class="section" id="overview">
  <h2 class="section-title"><span class="section-number">1.</span> Resumen de la auditoria</h2>

  <table class="info-table">
    <tbody>
      <tr>
        <th>Objetivo</th>
        <td><code>{{ target_locator }}</code></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <th>Tipo de objetivo</th>
        <td>{{ target_kind }}</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <th>Producer</th>
        <td><code>{{ producer }}</code></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <th>Inicio</th>
        <td>{{ started_at.isoformat(timespec='seconds') }}</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <th>Fin</th>
        <td>{{ finished_at.isoformat(timespec='seconds') }}</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <th>Duracion</th>
        <td>{{ '%.2f' % duration_seconds }} segundos</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <th>Hallazgos totales</th>
        <td><strong>{{ finding_total }}</strong></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <th>Metodologia</th>
        <td><code>{{ methodology_version }}</code></td>
      </tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <h3 class="subsection-title">Indice</h3>
  <ul class="toc-list">
    {% for entry in toc_entries %}
    <li class="toc-item">
      <span class="toc-number">{{ entry.num }}</span>
      <span class="toc-text">{{ entry.title }}</span>
    </li>
    {% endfor %}
  </ul>

  <div class="methodology-box">
    <div class="methodology-box-title">Nota metodologica</div>
    <p>
      ARGOS aplica una metodologia doble. Para configuraciones MCP estaticas
      evalua reglas determinitisticas (scanner). Para agentes en ejecucion
      envia una bateria de probes ASI01 a ASI10 mapeadas a la taxonomia
      OWASP Agentic AI Threats and Mitigations v1.0 (febrero 2025). Cada
      hallazgo conserva un rastro de evidencia suficiente para reproducir
      la deteccion, y se mapea automaticamente a los marcos de compliance
      aplicables (NIST AI RMF 1.0, EU AI Act 2024/1689, CSA AICM,
      ISO/IEC 42001:2023).
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
